data.enText: a group into which animals, plants, etc. that are able to breed with each other and produce healthy young are divided, smaller than a genus and identified by a Latin name
There are many species of dog(s).
a conservation area for endangered species

simple_means.memory_skill: speci 外观；种类 + es → 种类，物种

tr: (biology) taxonomic group whose members can interbreed

value.def: A species is a class of plants or animals whose members have the same main characteristics and are able to breed with each other.

example.ex: There are several thousand species of trees here.
